    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "It looks like our current API can't do that, because we encode the max message size as an int, so the maximum supported value is 2147483647.  Do you actually need to use a max size larger than that?  If so, we might need to make some API changes.\n\n@ctiller, what do you think about changing channel args to use long instead of int?\n"
